{"tid":295761,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"130kg男星Jonah Hill暴瘦 XL→S","createTime":"2017-06-24T04:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T09:05:31.000Z","uid":41453,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c41ee5f39351e48c343705e017827220160ea2d","tid":295761,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"好萊塢男星喬納希爾（Jonah Hill）在《華爾街之狼》的表現令人印象深刻，圓滾滾的模樣相當討喜，但是近1年來疑似積極使用激進的「溜溜球節食（Yo-yo dieting）」瘦身，近來被拍到甩肉成功，看起來超有型！<br />\n<br />\n喬納希爾2015年為了《火線掏寶》增重到130公斤，結束後便求救曾一起合作過《龍虎少年隊》的查寧塔圖（Channing Tatum）：「如果我少吃一點又運動健身，我會變瘦嗎？」好友便說：「廢話！這是全世界都知道最簡單的事！」所以他之後便改變飲食習慣，發現日式料理對他減重來說幫助很大，愛喝啤酒的他還一度求救營養師，「我會減肥，我會吃得更健康，但拜託教我怎麼同時可以享受喝啤酒。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，1年多前也有報導指出喬納希爾使用的是溜溜球節食，過程中用極端的方法控制飲食，能在短時間達到目的，但一段時間過去，如此方式會造成抑鬱症或疲勞等後遺症，而且無法持續很久，最後很容易又回到過去的飲食習慣，甚至吃得更多、更肥胖。<br />\n<br />\n但是喬納希爾似乎沒有胖回去，10日出現在美國洛杉磯街頭，留著招牌的絡腮鬍，穿著有點緊的短袖上衣，褲管還捲起來，從過去的小胖子變身成型男，乍看之下差點認不出來他是誰，手臂和胸部似乎都有些肌肉，讓網友驚呼變得好帥，可是也有不少粉絲希望他要注意健康，畢竟體重變化太劇烈對身體也是種負擔。<br />\n<img src=\"http://libertycitys.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/jonah-hill-fat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flibertycitys.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F04%2Fjonah-hill-fat.jpg&h=d43a7aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/assets.forward.com/images/cropped/screen-shot-2017-06-19-at-50503-pm-1497906368.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Fassets.forward.com%2Fimages%2Fcropped%2Fscreen-shot-2017-06-19-at-50503-pm-1497906368.png&h=013ad206&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1343f702a52109a72f93cb7fcc8f12863aa72339","tid":295761,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"28 jump street<br />\n唔肥仲邊有戲拍?"},{"pid":"53f710449631eb1f9621d75275a11acf12d92747","tid":295761,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"瘦左咁多d 皮又唔覺鬆"},{"pid":"dd06de35ebe9f1cf4227313f33745f1835aecb21","tid":295761,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:01:59.000Z","msg":"變咗奈威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff3db013fa6bf418ee3f196d2853e50f1edf474","tid":295761,"uid":1285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7246863230655a71fb9804f58bab89ade26b71a3","tid":295761,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲似Bradley Copper"},{"pid":"e4334ca2ed762e736585c849c5f08d09635ce9a3","tid":295761,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"完全冇咗諧星嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34db4e85c22b34c490c29831c8821e4f78baed40","tid":295761,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"左手紋身新紋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c93d6b35382e2d916288bc247441f761a5e2dc","tid":295761,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左手紋身新紋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}